&lt;p data-start=&quot;450&quot; data-end=&quot;809&quot;&gt;You think in time series, signals, and regimes.&lt;br&gt;You care about insight quality, not academic purity.&lt;br&gt;You want your models tested by markets, not papers.&lt;br&gt;If you dislike messy data and real-world constraints, this is not your role.&lt;/p&gt;
