&lt;p data-start=&quot;841&quot; data-end=&quot;1205&quot;&gt;You will build quantitative and ML-driven insight systems using structured time series data.&lt;br&gt;This role exists to turn raw financial data into actionable investor signals.&lt;br&gt;You will work closely with engineers to productionize quant logic.&lt;/p&gt;
