&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop models using structured financial time series&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build insight generation and scenario analysis pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with backend engineers to deploy models in production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate signals based on real investor outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve attribution and explainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
