&lt;p data-start=&quot;1897&quot; data-end=&quot;2014&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1897&quot; data-end=&quot;1916&quot;&gt;After 6 months:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1916&quot; data-end=&quot;1919&quot;&gt;Signals used by customers.&lt;/p&gt;
